                              Trashcan

        The Trashcan is a special drawer in each volume for storing files
that you no longer need and may wish to delete. Discard icons or
pseudo-icons for the files to be deleted by dragging them into the Trashcan
drawer. If the icon to be discarded is a drawer, its associated files are
also moved to the Trashcan.

        Choosing Empty Trash from the Icons menu deletes the icons and all
of their associated files from the Trashcan. Before choosing Empty Trash,
you can still recover any of the Trashcan's contents by opening its window
and dragging the icons back out.


